  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "grafana-postgresql-datasource", "uid": "postgresql" },
      "description": "Top 15 queries by mean execution time (snapshot since last pg_stat_statements_reset() — there is no time axis). Click a bar to filter the table below to that exact query; clear the 'Query filter (queryid)' box at the top to show all 100 again.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "custom": {
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "fillOpacity": 80,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          },
          "links": [
            {
              "title": "Filter table below by this query",
              "url": "?var-qid=${__data.fields.queryid}"
            }
          ],
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 100 },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 500 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 1000 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "ms"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "queryid" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "custom.hideFrom", "value": { "legend": true, "tooltip": true, "viz": true } }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 11, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "barRadius": 0,
        "barWidth": 0.8,
        "fullHighlight": false,
        "groupWidth": 0.7,
        "legend": { "calcs": [], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": false },
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "showValue": "auto",
        "stacking": "none",
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" },
        "xTickLabelRotation": 0,
        "xTickLabelSpacing": 0
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "grafana-postgresql-datasource", "uid": "postgresql" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "format": "table",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT\n  LEFT(regexp_replace(query, '\\s+', ' ', 'g'), 70) AS query,\n  ROUND(mean_exec_time::numeric, 2) AS mean_ms,\n  queryid::text AS queryid\nFROM pg_stat_statements\nWHERE query NOT ILIKE '%pg_stat_statements%'\n  AND query NOT ILIKE 'BEGIN%'\n  AND query NOT ILIKE 'COMMIT%'\n  AND query NOT ILIKE 'ROLLBACK%'\nORDER BY mean_exec_time DESC\nLIMIT 15",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Top 15 queries by mean execution time",
      "type": "barchart"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "grafana-postgresql-datasource", "uid": "postgresql" },
      "description": "Top 100 normalized queries by mean execution time. Stats accumulate since last pg_stat_statements_reset(). Filter excludes pg_stat_statements self-queries and trivial TX control.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": { "type": "auto" },
            "inspect": false
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }]
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "query" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "custom.width", "value": 600 }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "mean_ms" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "unit", "value": "ms" },
              { "id": "thresholds", "value": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 100 }, { "color": "orange", "value": 500 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1000 }] } },
              { "id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": { "type": "color-background" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "total_ms" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "unit", "value": "ms" }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "stddev_ms" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "unit", "value": "ms" }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "calls" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "unit", "value": "short" }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "rows" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "unit", "value": "short" }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 22, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 11 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": { "countRows": false, "fields": "", "reducer": ["sum"], "show": false },
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [{ "desc": true, "displayName": "mean_ms" }]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "grafana-postgresql-datasource", "uid": "postgresql" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "format": "table",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT \n  query,\n  calls,\n  ROUND(mean_exec_time::numeric, 2) AS mean_ms,\n  ROUND(total_exec_time::numeric, 2) AS total_ms,\n  ROUND(stddev_exec_time::numeric, 2) AS stddev_ms,\n  rows\nFROM pg_stat_statements\nWHERE query NOT ILIKE '%pg_stat_statements%'\n  AND query NOT ILIKE 'BEGIN%'\n  AND query NOT ILIKE 'COMMIT%'\n  AND query NOT ILIKE 'ROLLBACK%'\n  AND (${qid:sqlstring} = '' OR queryid::text = ${qid:sqlstring})\nORDER BY mean_exec_time DESC\nLIMIT 100",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Top 100 queries by mean execution time",
      "type": "table"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" },
      "description": "How to reset the stats window.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 33 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "### Reset stats\n\nThe table above shows aggregated stats since the **last reset** (or since `pg_stat_statements` was installed). To get a fresh \"last N days\" window, reset the stats:\n\n```sql\nSELECT pg_stat_statements_reset();\n```\n\nRun inside the BPP database (e.g. `make dbshell-psql`). Reset is global per database (or per user/query if arguments are supplied — see [PostgreSQL docs](https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/pgstatstatements.html#PGSTATSTATEMENTS-FUNCS)).\n\nNo automatic reset cron is configured — choose a cadence that matches how you want to interpret \"mean execution time\" (e.g. weekly, after each release, never).",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.0.0",
      "title": "Reset stats",
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
